  "texts": [
    "Fifty-six students answered that they have not tried any of them.",
    "This group was chosen for the evaluation, since for them no bias should be present.",
    "Among them, 13 were not able to participate for personal reasons, whereas 43 took part at the experiment.",
    "The training and evaluation of the ML algorithms were carried out on the 1217 questionnaire answers that passed the selection procedure exposed in the \"Prediction algorithm design\" section.",
    "As said in the \"Preprocessing of the data\" section, tool T4 was excluded from the analysis since more than 15% of the participants did not know it."
